# Zero-Environment Architecture
# The app no longer relies on build-time environment variables for connectivity.
# All Google Apps Script (GAS) routing urls are dynamically configured per-tenant 
# during the Onboarding flow or via Invitation Links, persisting in secure LocalStorage.

